cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and social media data analysis to determine the veracity of rumors. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with natural language processing. The paper also uses statistical modeling and machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). The paper also deals with information retrieval and classification, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
